headline: EA to Release Fourth Quarter and Fiscal Year 2025 Results on May 6, 2025
summary: REDWOOD CITY, Calif., April 15, 2025--Electronic Arts Inc. (NASDAQ: EA) will release its financial results for the fiscal quarter and fiscal year ended March 31, 2025 after the close of market on Tuesday, May 6, 2025. In conjunction with this release, EA will host a conference call to review its financial results for the fiscal quarter and fiscal year, discuss its outlook for the future and may disclose other material developments affecting its business and/or financial performance.
